:"/notes-0","page_id":"/notes","type":"text","url":"/notes","content":"Welcome to the docs!"},"3":{"id":"/notes/misc","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"page","content":"杂记","url":"/notes/misc"},"4":{"id":"/notes/misc-0","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"pnpm add 与 pnpm install 无区别，从语义上来说，添加新依赖更推荐 pnpm add"},"5":{"id":"/notes/misc-1","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Fumadocs 与 Next.js 同样是很有个性的框架，它们带来新颖特性的同时也可能会带来意外的错误，需要自行评估使用"},"6":{"id":"/notes/misc-2","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"git fetch 是只获取更新，而 git pull 是获取并合并更新"},"7":{"id":"/notes/misc-3","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"比特币不具有图灵完备性，比特币只是价值存储系统，以太坊想要成为一个完整的工具。"},"8":{"id":"/notes/misc-4","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"混合智能合约"},"9":{"id":"/notes/misc-5","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"一个 dApp 通常是多个智能合约的组合"},"10":{"id":"/notes/misc-6","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"我们需要从 Brand Based 的理念转为 Math Based。"},"11":{"id":"/notes/misc-7","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"钱包的助记词可以访问整个钱包，钱包可以创建多个账户，钱包的助记词需要仔细保管！账户的私钥只能访问单个账户。"},"12":{"id":"/notes/misc-8","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Transaction Fee 和 Gas Price："},"13":{"id":"/notes/misc-9","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"计算越复杂，Gas 越高"},"14":{"id":"/notes/misc-10","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Gwei = 1 ETH * 10^-9 ，Gwei 作为单位本身是不变的"},"15":{"id":"/notes/misc-11","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Gas Price 是你愿意为 Gas 消耗支付多少 Gwei，通常来说，Gas Price 越高（例如 50 Gwei），交易优先级更高（50 Gwei 比 10 Gwei 更受矿工青睐）"},"16":{"id":"/notes/misc-12","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Nonce（Number Only Used Once，随机数） 是一个用于防止交易重放攻击和保证交易顺序的计数器。"},"17":{"id":"/notes/misc-13","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"地址并不完全等同于公钥，但它是从公钥经过一系列哈希变换生成的。可以理解为地址是公钥的\"压缩\"版本，它的设计目的是为了更短、更安全地表示公钥。"},"18":{"id":"/notes/misc-14","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"说“比特币通过PoW运作”是不够精准的，准确的表述应该是： 👉 “比特币通过中本聪共识运作，PoW 是其中的关键组成部分。”"},"19":{"id":"/notes/misc-15","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"中本聪共识 是比特币网络达成共识的完整机制，包括："},"20":{"id":"/notes/misc-16","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"PoW（工作量证明） 作为竞争记账权的方式。"},"21":{"id":"/notes/misc-17","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"最长链原则（Longest Chain Rule）：节点选择计算量最高的链作为有效链。"},"22":{"id":"/notes/misc-18","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"经济激励 机制：矿工因挖矿获得区块奖励和交易手续费，激励他们诚实工作。"},"23":{"id":"/notes/misc-19","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"PoW ≠ 比特币共识机制，PoW 只是比特币实现共识的手段之一，它用于："},"24":{"id":"/notes/misc-20","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"竞争区块打包权。"},"25":{"id":"/notes/misc-21","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"确保新区块的产生符合数学难度规则。"},"26":{"id":"/notes/misc-22","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"保护网络免受女巫攻击和恶意篡改。"},"27":{"id":"/notes/misc-23","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"比特币减半机制是通过代码内置的算法实现的："},"28":{"id":"/notes/misc-24","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"每开采210,000个区块（约4年）进行一次奖励减半"},"29":{"id":"/notes/misc-25","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"减半机制确保了比特币的稀缺性"},"30":{"id":"/notes/misc-26","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"最终总量将趋近于2100万枚，但永远不会完全达到"},"31":{"id":"/notes/misc-27","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"矿工收入将逐步从\"区块奖励\"转向\"交易手续费\"为主"},"32":{"id":"/notes/misc-28","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"区块链扩容层级结构可以这样理解："},"33":{"id":"/notes/misc-29","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Layer 1 (基础层):"},"34":{"id":"/notes/misc-30","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"主区块链网络本身，如比特币、以太坊主网"},"35":{"id":"/notes/misc-31","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"负责最终的交易结算与安全保障"},"36":{"id":"/notes/misc-32","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"拥有完整的去中心化特性，但吞吐量有限"},"37":{"id":"/notes/misc-33","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Layer 2 (扩展层):"},"38":{"id":"/notes/misc-34","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"建立在Layer 1之上的扩展解决方案"},"39":{"id":"/notes/misc-35","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"在链外处理大量交易，定期将结果提交到Layer 1"},"40":{"id":"/notes/misc-36","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"继承Layer 1安全性，同时提高性能、降低费用"},"41":{"id":"/notes/misc-37","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Rollup (卷叠技术):"},"42":{"id":"/notes/misc-38","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Layer 2的主要实现方式之一，与侧链(Sidechains)等非Rollup等方案相比，安全性较高"},"43":{"id":"/notes/misc-39","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"将多笔交易\"打包\"处理后，只向主链提交概要数据"},"44":{"id":"/notes/misc-40","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"分两种类型："},"45":{"id":"/notes/misc-41","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Optimistic Rollup (乐观卷叠): 假设交易有效，有争议期(通常7天)，如Optimism、Arbitrum"},"46":{"id":"/notes/misc-42","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"ZK-Rollup (零知识卷叠): 使用数学证明验证交易有效性，无需争议期，如zkSync、StarkNet"},"47":{"id":"/notes/misc-43","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"通俗比喻：如果把区块链比作交通系统"},"48":{"id":"/notes/misc-44","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Layer 1 是主干道：安全但容易拥堵"},"49":{"id":"/notes/misc-45","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Layer 2 是快速辅路：分流主干道交通"},"50":{"id":"/notes/misc-46","page_id":"/notes/misc","type":"text","url":"/notes/misc","content":"Rollup 是公交车：一次运送多人，只占一个车位的空间"},"51":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"page","content":"中国法律位阶","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law"},"52":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-0","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"对中国法律位阶的概述"},"53":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-1","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"heading","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law#参考资料","content":"参考资料"},"54":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-2","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"中国大陆的法律体系，按照效力位阶，可大致分为以下几个层级：宪法、法律、行政法规、地方性法规、规章。宪法是根本大法，具有最高的法律效力，其他法律都不能与宪法相抵触。\n以下是具体层级及其制定机关："},"55":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-3","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"宪法:\n《中华人民共和国宪法》是国家的根本大法，是其他一切法律的立法依据和基础。"},"56":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-4","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"法律:\n由全国人民代表大会(全国人大)及其常务委员会制定，如《中华人民共和国民法典》、《中华人民共和国刑法》等。"},"57":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-5","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"行政法规:\n由国务院制定，是对法律的具体化和补充，如《中华人民共和国食品安全法实施条例》。"},"58":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-6","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"地方性法规:\n由省级和设区的市级人民代表大会及其常务委员会制定，在各自的行政区域内施行，如《上海市生活垃圾管理条例》。"},"59":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-7","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"规章:\n包括部门规章和地方政府规章，部门规章由国务院各部委制定，地方政府规章由地方各级人民政府制定。\n此外，还有一些特殊类型的法律，如自治条例和单行条例，它们在民族自治地方和经济特区具有特殊法律地位。法律效力层级的高低，决定了在具体适用法律时的优先顺序，下位法必须服从上位法。"},"60":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-8","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law#参考资料","content":"中华人民共和国法律位阶 - 维基百科"},"61":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-9","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law#参考资料","content":"法律位阶 - 百度百科"},"62":{"id":"/notes/civil-service","page_id":"/notes/civil-service","type":"page","content":"行测笔记","url":"/notes/civil-service"},"63":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs","type":"page","content":"使用 Fumadocs 搭建文档网站","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs"},"64":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs","content":"Fumadocs 是一款开源文档框架，通过 Next.js 实现。"},"65":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fumadocs","content":"Fumadocs 是 GitHub 社区里一款比较新颖的文档框架，相比于其他已有的框架（Docusaurus、VitePress\n等），它的默认 UI 质感非常好，同时深度集成了 Next.js 的特性，可以尝鲜部署一下。"},"66":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab","type":"page","content":"折腾笔记","url":"/notes/geek-lab"},"67":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"page","content":"使用 Fumadocs 搭建博客","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs"},"68":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","content":"Making a Blog with Fumadocs 的译文"},"69":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#概述","content":"概述"},"70":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-2","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#配置内容","content":"配置内容"},"71":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-3","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#构建-ui-布局","content":"构建 UI 布局"},"72":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-4","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客索引页面","content":"创建博客索引页面"},"73":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-5","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客正文页面","content":"创建博客正文页面"},"74":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-6","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#配置元数据","content":"配置元数据"},"75":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-7","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#write-posts","content":"撰写帖子"},"76":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-8","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","content":"type: success"},"77":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-9","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","content":"本文是天明个人翻译的小指南，原文链接：https://fumadocs.dev/blog/make-a-blog"},"78":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-10","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","content":"Fumadocs 是一个文档框架，它基于 Next.js 构建了一个强大的内容管理系统。我们可以使用 Fumadocs 在单个 Next.js\n应用程序上构建博客站点和文档。"},"79":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-11","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#概述","content":"本指南可帮助我们使用 Fumadocs 和 Fumadocs MDX 构建博客站点。"},"80":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-12","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#概述","content":"理解需要一定的前置知识准备，包括 Next.js 和 Fumadocs 的基础知识。"},"81":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-13","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#概述","content":"我们将使用 Fumadocs MDX 来管理内容，并使用 Tailwind CSS 和 Fumadocs UI 实现我们自己的 UI。"},"82":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-14","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#配置内容","content":"定义一个 blogPosts （博客帖子）集合。"},"83":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-15","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#配置内容","content":"在 source.ts 中解析并输出集合："},"84":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-16","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#配置内容","content":"我们现在可以从 blog 中访问博客内容。"},"85":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-17","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客索引页面","content":"默认情况下，应该有一个 (home) 路由组，里面有 <HomeLayout />\n组件。让我们把博客页面放在它下面，这样我们就可以在我们的博客网站上获得漂亮的导航栏。"},"86":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-18","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客索引页面","content":"title: 小提示"},"87":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-19","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客索引页面","content":"像 text-fd-muted-foreground 这样的颜色来自 Fumadocs UI 的设计系统，我们也可以使用自己的颜色，或者使用\nShadcn UI。"},"88":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-20","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客正文页面","content":"请注意，博客文章不会有像 /slug1/slug2 这样的嵌套路径段，我们不需要为博客文章提供包罗万象的路由。"},"89":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-21","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客正文页面","content":"在 Next.js 中，[slug] 对应的是单层动态路由，[[...slug]] 可选捕获所有路由，这里我们用的是前者。"},"90":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-22","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#write-posts","content":"UI 现在已经完成了，我们可以在 content/blog 目录下写一些博文，比如："},"91":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-23","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#write-posts","content":"使用 next dev 启动开发服务器后，我们应该会在 /blog 路由下看到博客文章。"},"92":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","type":"page","content":"MDX","url":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx"},"93":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","content":"一种为 Markdown 插入组件的标记语言"},"94":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","content":"官网：https://mdxjs.com/"},"95":{"id":"/notes/coding","page_id":"/notes/coding","type":"page","content":"Hello Code!","url":"/notes/coding"},"96":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"page","content":"认识数据库","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse"},"97":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-0","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据","content":"数据"},"98":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-1","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库","content":"数据库"},"99":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-2","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库系统","content":"数据库系统"},"100":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-3","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"数据库管理系统"},"101":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-4","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#结论","content":"结论"},"102":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-5","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","content":"数据库中常见的基本概念如下。"},"103":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-6","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据","content":"数据是对客观事物、事件的记录与描述，也是对客观事物的逻辑归纳。数据可以是连续的，如声音、图像等，也可以是离散的，如符号、文字等。"},"104":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-7","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库","content":"数据库（Database，DB）是存储在计算机内、有组织的、可共享的相关数据的集合，这种集合按一定的数据模型组织、描述并长期存储，同时能够以安全可靠的方法对数据进行检索。"},"105":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-8","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库系统","content":"数据库系统（Database System，DBS）是指在计算机系统中引入数据库后的系统。它主要由数据库、数据库用户、计算机硬件系统和计算机软件系统（含数据库管理系统）等几部分组成。"},"106":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-9","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"数据库管理系统（Database Management System，DBMS）是指建立、运用、管理和维护数据库，并对数据库进行统一控制的系统软件。"},"107":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-10","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/l